title: Veasna - Energy (2016)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Energy is the debut album from German Goa trance producer and artist Veasna. He made his initial appearance on the Celestial Transvibrations compilation from Neogoa Records in late 2014. During the last two years he worked very hard to finish his album and test new material at various Goa trance gatherings. Now it’s finally here and it will bring so much needed energy to any dance floor.  Download Energy - http://www.neogoa.net/energy/

Tracklist:

01 – Pulsar (143 BPM)
02 – You Have Rights (144 BPM)
03 – Rubix (145 BPM)
04 – Hex (147 BPM)
05 – Godspeed (145 BPM)
06 – Showdown! (145 BPM)
07 – Three (147 BPM)
08 – Termination Shock (147 BPM)
09 – Ultraviolet (149 BPM) *
10 – The Essence Of Energy (90 BPM)

* – bonus CD track
